RegisterUser - Class in edu.neu.ccis.sms.servlets
Servlet implementation class RegisterUser; This servlet takes form attributes for user-registration and create a new user into SMS system Takes 6 request attributes - 1) username - username to be used by user for logging in to the SMS system 2) firstname - first name of user 3) lastname - last name of user 4) email id - email id of user - this should be a unique email id 5) password - password for user 6) confirmPassword - To make sure that user has put confirmed the password Note - This is just user creation servlet; registering a user to members is not part of this servlet; for that user should login first, and access register-member UI page.
